WEBVTT

00:03.069 --> 00:04.571
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON</i>
<i>"NECESSARY ROUGHNESS"...</i>

00:05.505 --> 00:06.439
BRICKHOUSE LINGERIE
WAS MY IDEA FIRST,

00:07.307 --> 00:09.075
SO SHE HAS NO RIGHT
TO PITCH THIS TO YOU

00:09.109 --> 00:09.909
WITHOUT MY CONSENT.

00:10.777 --> 00:11.378
I HOPE YOU TWO
LIKE WORKING TOGETHER,

00:11.945 --> 00:13.046
BECAUSE THIS IS GOOD.

00:14.047 --> 00:14.748
FROM THIS POINT FORWARD,
WE'RE OFFICIALLY AT WAR.

00:14.781 --> 00:17.250
THE ENEMY --
SBG MANAGEMENT.

00:17.283 --> 00:20.520
I'M ABIGAIL BRUCE,
MANAGING PARTNER AT SBG.

00:20.553 --> 00:21.554
BRUCE? WHO'S BRUCE?

00:21.588 --> 00:23.490
CONNOR'S FORMER ASSISTANT.

00:23.523 --> 00:26.426
WHY DID TROY INSTALL HIS OWN
SECURITY SYSTEM ON TOP OF V3's?

00:26.459 --> 00:28.395
OUR HACKER IS INSIDE
V3's SECURE NETWORK.

00:28.428 --> 00:29.863
JUST LET HIM
DO HIS THING.

00:29.896 --> 00:31.331
SAM CONTE
FROM THE L.A. OFFICE.

00:31.364 --> 00:32.198
PLEASURE.

00:32.232 --> 00:33.266
NICE FLOWERS.

00:33.299 --> 00:34.100
FROM SOMEBODY SPECIAL?

00:36.136 --> 00:38.171
IT'S BEEN
A REALLY ROUGH YEAR.

00:38.204 --> 00:39.172
LET ME MAKE IT BETTER.

00:45.278 --> 00:46.880
Dani: NO, JEANETTE!

00:46.913 --> 00:50.116
IT WAS NOT
A ONE-NIGHT STAND.

00:50.150 --> 00:52.185
IT WAS A TWO-NIGHT STAND.

00:52.218 --> 00:54.254
[ LAUGHS ]
I KNOW!

00:54.287 --> 00:57.123
I KNOW IT'S NOT
LIKE ME AT ALL,

00:57.157 --> 01:01.594
BUT IT WAS EXACTLY
WHAT THIS DOCTOR ORDERED.

01:01.628 --> 01:05.365
WELL, THE JOB IS GOOD.

01:05.398 --> 01:08.401
KIDS -- GOOD.

01:08.435 --> 01:11.171
I AM GOOD.

01:11.204 --> 01:14.541
YEAH, I FEEL LIKE THINGS
ARE FINALLY...

01:14.574 --> 01:17.677
FALLING INTO PLACE.

01:22.649 --> 01:24.384
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

01:25.952 --> 01:29.189
MORNING. NON-FAT
EXTRA-FOAM CAPPUCCINO.

01:29.222 --> 01:30.657
MY, GOD.
COULD YOU BE MORE EFFICIENT?

01:30.690 --> 01:31.691
I HOPE NOT.

01:31.725 --> 01:32.759
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

01:32.792 --> 01:34.494
SO, WHAT'S ON TOP
FOR TODAY?

01:34.527 --> 01:36.229
STAFF MEETING AT 9:00.
MM-HMM.

01:36.262 --> 01:37.464
NEW CLIENT LUNCH
AT NOON.
UH-HUH.

01:37.497 --> 01:38.732
BARNEYS PRIVATE SALE
AT 7:00.

01:38.765 --> 01:40.600
OOH, GOOD TO KNOW.

01:40.633 --> 01:43.169
OH, SPEAKING OF THINGS
YOU MIGHT WANT TO KNOW.

01:43.203 --> 01:43.670
OH.

01:43.703 --> 01:44.938
SAM, HEY.

01:44.971 --> 01:46.239
YOU'RE BACK IN TOWN.

01:46.272 --> 01:47.607
YEAH,
FOR THE V3 CHARITY EVENT.

01:47.640 --> 01:48.775
OH.

01:48.808 --> 01:50.577
I WAS SUPPOSED TO RSVP
TO THAT.

01:50.610 --> 01:52.579
OH, YOU DID -- I'LL HAVE DRESS
AND SHOE OPTIONS FOR YOU

01:52.612 --> 01:53.413
BY LUNCH TOMORROW.

01:53.446 --> 01:55.215
THANK YOU.

01:55.248 --> 01:56.349
I SHOULD HAVE CALLED.

01:56.383 --> 01:57.417
IT WAS LAST MINUTE.

01:57.450 --> 01:58.485
DID YOU LIKE
THE FLOWERS?

01:58.518 --> 02:00.220
YES, I DID.
THANK YOU.

02:00.253 --> 02:00.987
THEY WERE BEAUTIFUL.

02:01.821 --> 02:02.322
PEOPLE KEPT ASKING ME
WHO DIED.

02:02.956 --> 02:04.391
HOPEFULLY NOT ME.
MM.

02:04.424 --> 02:05.725
LISTEN, I'M IN TOWN
FOR A COUPLE WEEKS.

02:05.759 --> 02:08.228
I WAS HOPING WE COULD
SEE SOME OF EACH OTHER.

02:08.261 --> 02:09.396
YES, PLEASE.

02:10.497 --> 02:11.364
GREAT -- I'LL SET UP DINNER
WITH YOUR NOSY ASSISTANT,

02:12.132 --> 02:12.165
WHO'S LOOKING AT US
RIGHT NOW.

02:13.233 --> 02:15.402
WHAT, DO YOU HAVE EYES
IN THE BACK OF YOUR HEAD?

02:15.435 --> 02:16.603
I'M AN AGENT --
YOU GOT TO HAVE

02:17.704 --> 02:18.038
EYES IN THE BACK OF YOUR HEAD
IF YOU WANT TO SURVIVE.

02:18.071 --> 02:19.572
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:23.443 --> 02:24.811
SEX APPEAL...

02:24.844 --> 02:26.246
THE "X" FACTOR,
CHEMISTRY --

02:26.279 --> 02:27.480
WHATEVER
YOU WANT TO CALL IT,

02:27.514 --> 02:28.982
YOU TWO HAVE IT,
AND EVERYBODY WANTS IT.

02:29.015 --> 02:30.483
IT'S A MATCH
MADE IN PRIME TIME.

02:30.517 --> 02:32.419
WELL, THIS MATCH
DONE BURNED DOWN.

02:32.452 --> 02:35.455
LOOK, I REALIZE THAT SHEERA
MAY HAVE JUMPED THE GUN

02:35.488 --> 02:37.791
DUE TO HER
UNBRIDLED ENTHUSIASM,

02:37.824 --> 02:39.559
BUT GOOD IDEAS ARE HARD
TO COME BY,

02:39.592 --> 02:41.494
SO KISS AND MAKE UP.

02:41.528 --> 02:43.329
COME ON.

02:45.031 --> 02:48.201
FOR THE SAKE
OF MY FINANCIAL FUTURE...

02:49.602 --> 02:51.571
...I'M ON BOARD.
VERY GOOD.

02:51.604 --> 02:53.573
BUT THERE WILL BE NO MORE
OF THIS UNBRIDLED ENTHUSIASM

02:53.606 --> 02:56.242
UNLESS I AM THE ONE
BRIDLING IT.

02:56.276 --> 02:58.645
ABSOLUTELY, T.K.
PARTNERS, 50/50.

02:58.678 --> 02:59.813
60/40 -- MY IDEA.

02:59.846 --> 03:01.648
UH, MY IDEA
TO PARTNER UP.

03:01.681 --> 03:03.249
YIN AND YANG.

03:03.283 --> 03:05.485
PLUS, I SOLD IT
TO CONNOR IN THE ROOM.

03:05.518 --> 03:06.553
YOU ONLY SOLD IT
'CAUSE YOU STOLE IT.

03:06.586 --> 03:07.721
55/45.

03:07.754 --> 03:08.588
DEAL.

03:08.621 --> 03:09.689
GOOD.

03:09.723 --> 03:10.857
WHO NEEDS LAWYERS?

03:10.890 --> 03:13.259
LET'S HAVE A HANDSHAKE.

03:13.293 --> 03:14.361
NOT ME. COME ON.

03:14.394 --> 03:15.762
SHAKE WITH HER.

03:15.795 --> 03:17.464
THERE WE GO.

03:17.497 --> 03:19.265
COME ON.

03:19.299 --> 03:20.033
GOOD.

03:20.066 --> 03:21.601
NOW, I WANT TO SEE
YOU TWO

03:21.634 --> 03:22.602
OUT IN PUBLIC TOGETHER.

03:22.635 --> 03:23.403
I WANT YOU ON RED CARPETS,

03:24.437 --> 03:25.638
STARTING WITH
V3's BIG GALA, OKAY?

03:25.672 --> 03:27.374
BRANGELINA. HA!

03:27.407 --> 03:29.609
EVERYONE'S GONNA BE
TALKING ABOUT SHE-K.
[chic]

03:29.642 --> 03:31.811
* WEAR SHE-K
AND GET FREAKY *

03:31.845 --> 03:33.279
WHAT?

03:33.313 --> 03:34.280
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
"SHE-KAY."

03:36.049 --> 03:37.584
T.K.!

03:37.617 --> 03:39.052
T.K., WAIT.

03:39.085 --> 03:40.587
THAT'S MR. KING
TO YOU, MS. KANE.

03:40.620 --> 03:41.588
OH, COME ON.

03:41.621 --> 03:42.622
I'VE ALREADY
APOLOGIZED TWICE.

03:42.655 --> 03:43.690
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO DO?

03:44.624 --> 03:44.657
YOU WANT ME TO BEG
FOR YOUR FORGIVENESS?

03:45.058 --> 03:46.326
YEAH. I DO.

03:46.359 --> 03:47.460
YOU KNOW WHAT?

03:47.494 --> 03:48.762
WE'RE JUST BUSINESS PARTNERS
IN THIS,

03:48.795 --> 03:50.430
SO LET'S JUST KEEP THIS
WHOLE THING PROFESSIONAL.

03:50.463 --> 03:51.398
NO!

03:52.232 --> 03:54.501
I DON'T WANT TO LOSE YOU
TO BRICKHOUSE.

03:54.534 --> 03:58.772
SO CAN WE JUST GO SOMEWHERE
AND TALK THIS THROUGH?

03:58.805 --> 04:00.640
[ SIGHS ]
HEY, MAYBE I CAN...

04:00.674 --> 04:03.410
BEG YOU IN PRIVATE.

04:05.578 --> 04:07.647
YOU KNOW WHAT?

04:07.681 --> 04:09.382
IF I AM LATE TO PRACTICE,

04:09.416 --> 04:11.418
COACH WILL GRILL MY ASS
ON A HIBACHI.

04:11.451 --> 04:13.553
THE MAN IS ABOUT AS FLEXIBLE
AS A CROWBAR.

04:16.456 --> 04:19.659
Even five minutes?

04:19.693 --> 04:21.528
For a hot drink?

04:21.561 --> 04:22.862
It's my treat.

04:22.896 --> 04:26.399
Connor: FRIENDS,
'TIS THE SEASON FOR GIVING.

04:26.433 --> 04:27.834
I'M NOT TALKING ABOUT
HOLIDAY BONUSES.

04:27.867 --> 04:28.902
I'M TALKING ABOUT
GIVING BACK.

04:28.935 --> 04:31.471
CARL WEBBER,
MASTER MONEY MAN,

04:31.504 --> 04:32.872
PLEASE TELL ME THIS YEAR
IS GONNA BE A BIG YEAR

04:32.906 --> 04:34.474
FOR THE V3 FOUNDATION.

04:34.507 --> 04:36.910
IT'S GONNA BE A BIG YEAR
FOR THE V3 FOUNDATION.

04:36.943 --> 04:37.877
AND HE'S FUNNY,
TOO, HUH?

04:37.911 --> 04:39.713
[ LAUGHTER ]

04:39.746 --> 04:41.781
FOR THOSE OF YOU NEW TO V3,

04:41.815 --> 04:43.483
CARL IS OUR VICE PRESIDENT
OF ACCOUNTING,

04:43.516 --> 04:45.518
HE'S OUR ROCK OF GIBRALTAR,

04:45.552 --> 04:47.620
AND HE'S ALSO THE HEAD
OF OUR CHARITABLE FOUNDATION.

04:47.654 --> 04:49.689
CARL, I WANT YOU TO WALK US
THROUGH SATURDAY NIGHT.

04:49.723 --> 04:50.690
RIGHT. OKAY.

04:50.724 --> 04:52.559
SO, UH...

04:52.592 --> 04:55.428
LIKE LAST YEAR,
WE'RE GONNA HAVE A RED CARPET,

04:55.462 --> 04:57.764
MEDIA BLITZ,
AND A SILENT AUCTION.

04:57.797 --> 05:00.567
MOST OF OUR A-LISTERS
HAVE RSVP'd "YEA."

05:00.600 --> 05:01.901
UH, CLOONEY
SENT HIS REGRETS,

05:01.935 --> 05:03.570
ALONG WITH A SIZABLE CHECK.

05:03.603 --> 05:05.672
HE'LL BE IN ITALY,
ENJOYING HIS LIFE.

05:05.705 --> 05:06.740
BOO-HOO.

05:06.773 --> 05:07.941
[ LAUGHTER ]

05:07.974 --> 05:10.577
WE EXPECT TO RAISE BETWEEN
$2 AND $3 MILLION

05:10.610 --> 05:12.846
SPLIT EVENLY BETWEEN
OUR EIGHT NONPROFITS.

05:12.879 --> 05:15.582
AROUND 9:00,
I'LL TAKE THE STAGE,

05:15.615 --> 05:18.852
INTRODUCE CONNOR AS, UH,
A FINE HUMANITARIAN,

05:18.885 --> 05:20.553
BLAH, BLAH,
BLAH, BLAH.

05:21.755 --> 05:22.722
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE HOOKED UP TO
A LIE DETECTOR, ARE YOU, CARL?

05:22.756 --> 05:23.723
HEY, HEY!

05:23.757 --> 05:24.924
HEY!

05:24.958 --> 05:25.992
Carl:
I PLEAD THE FIFTH.

05:26.026 --> 05:28.728
ANYWAY, I HOPE YOU CAN
ALL JOIN US.

05:28.762 --> 05:30.530
IT'S, UH, IT'S GONNA BE,

05:30.563 --> 05:31.631
AS ALWAYS,
ONE HELL OF A NIGHT.
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

05:31.664 --> 05:32.899
THANKS, CARL -- LISTEN,

05:32.932 --> 05:35.869
IF IT'S ONE THING
WE DO RIGHT, WE DO GOOD.

05:35.902 --> 05:37.671
Troy: WHAT THE HELL'S
GOING ON?

05:39.873 --> 05:42.475
SPECIAL AGENT JENKINS,
FBI.

05:42.509 --> 05:43.777
ALL RIGHT, EVERYONE.
I NEED TO SEE YOUR HANDS.

05:43.810 --> 05:44.878
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

05:44.911 --> 05:45.779
NOW.

06:04.164 --> 06:07.033
* HURRICANE-CANE-CANE COMING

06:08.001 --> 06:10.170
* THERE'S A HURRICANE-CANE-CANE
COMING *

06:10.203 --> 06:13.073
* HURRICANE-CANE-CANE COMING

06:13.106 --> 06:16.509
* THERE'S A HURRICANE-CANE-CANE
COMING *

06:16.543 --> 06:17.944
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

06:21.147 --> 06:23.483
FBI.
PLEASE STEP OUT.

06:23.516 --> 06:25.151
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
YOU WERE 18?

06:25.185 --> 06:26.219
YEAH, VERY FUNNY.

06:26.252 --> 06:27.120
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
COME ON.

06:27.887 --> 06:28.455
LET'S GO TAKE A SEAT
IN THE LOBBY.

06:28.988 --> 06:29.589
WHAT?
[ LAUGHS ]

06:30.523 --> 06:31.558
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
WHAT THE HELL IS GOING --

06:32.559 --> 06:32.592
WAIT. WAIT. HOLD ON.
DO YOU KNOW WHO WE ARE?

06:33.093 --> 06:34.094
YES, MR. KING, I DO,

06:35.061 --> 06:35.095
AND YOU ALSO NEED TO TAKE A SEAT
IN THE LOBBY.

06:35.462 --> 06:36.930
[ LAUGHS ]

06:37.997 --> 06:39.499
LISTEN, UM...IF I DON'T
GET MY ASS TO PRACTICE,

06:40.800 --> 06:41.901
THE ONLY PLACE I'M SITTING COME
SUNDAY IS ON THE BENCH, OKAY?

06:42.635 --> 06:43.570
SO, MAYBE I CAN,
UH, WORK OUT

06:44.704 --> 06:45.438
SOME SORT OF "GET OUT OF JAIL
FREE" CARD, YOU KNOW?

06:46.006 --> 06:46.506
50-YARD-LINE TICKETS?

06:47.040 --> 06:48.908
PRIMO SPOTS.
HMM.

06:48.942 --> 06:50.810
YOU TRYING TO BRIBE
A FEDERAL OFFICER?

06:52.078 --> 06:54.180
NO...

06:54.214 --> 06:56.950
YOU KNOW, I THINK WE'LL JUST
WAIT IN THE LOBBY.

06:56.983 --> 07:01.121
* HURRICANE-CANE-CANE COMING

07:01.154 --> 07:02.489
ALL RIGHT, SO, LET ME
GET THIS STRAIGHT.

07:03.723 --> 07:05.191
THE FBI CAN JUST WALTZ INTO
MY PRIVATE PLACE OF BUSINESS,

07:05.225 --> 07:07.660
COLLECT EVIDENCE
OF ALLEGED WRONGDOING,

07:07.694 --> 07:08.895
AND -- AND NOT EVEN
HAVE TO TELL US

07:08.928 --> 07:10.163
WHAT THE INVESTIGATION
IS ABOUT?

07:10.196 --> 07:11.865
AND WE CAN'T EVEN
CALL A LAWYER

07:11.898 --> 07:13.600
AS THEY WALK AWAY
WITH OUR FILES

07:13.633 --> 07:14.901
AND ANYTHING ELSE
THEY CAN PLUG INTO A SOCKET?

07:14.934 --> 07:16.202
SEALED WARRANT.

07:16.236 --> 07:17.604
THEY HAVE NO LEGAL OBLIGATION
TO TELL YOU

07:18.805 --> 07:19.572
THE TARGET OF INVESTIGATION
UNTIL INDICTMENTS ARE ISSUED.

07:19.606 --> 07:21.608
SO WE MIGHT NOT EVEN
BE THE TARGET.

07:21.641 --> 07:23.543
THEY MAY JUST BE LOOKING
FOR SOMETHING IN OUR FILES.

07:23.576 --> 07:25.145
POSSIBLY.
ALL RIGHT,
STAY ON IT, NICO.

07:25.178 --> 07:26.680
Dani: LISTEN --
THESE ARE PRIVILEGED,

07:26.713 --> 07:28.214
PERSONAL PATIENT FILES.

07:28.248 --> 07:30.083
MA'AM,
PLEASE STEP ASIDE.

07:30.116 --> 07:31.017
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY, DANI.

07:31.051 --> 07:33.253
YOUR FILES -- THEY'RE --
THEY'RE PROTECTED.

07:33.286 --> 07:35.121
HOW, EXACTLY?
THEY'RE BEING CARTED AWAY.

07:35.155 --> 07:35.955
JUST TEMPORARILY.

07:37.023 --> 07:38.558
THERE'S A CLEAN TEAM
AND A DIRTY TEAM.

07:38.591 --> 07:40.226
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
LIKE, LAUNDRY?

07:40.260 --> 07:43.096
THE DIRTY TEAM'S JOB
IS TO GO THROUGH EVERYTHING,

07:43.129 --> 07:44.964
AND THEN THEY DELIVER
TO THE CLEAN TEAM

07:44.998 --> 07:46.166
ONLY THE INFORMATION
THAT'S COVERED

07:46.199 --> 07:47.100
UNDER THE SEARCH WARRANT.

07:47.133 --> 07:48.868
WHICH IS WHAT?

07:48.902 --> 07:51.071
THAT I DON'T KNOW.
IT'S SEALED.

07:51.104 --> 07:53.573
BUT I AM PRETTY SURE
THE FBI DIDN'T RAID V3

07:53.606 --> 07:55.108
TO FIND OUT
HOW CINDY LUCK IS DOING.

07:55.141 --> 07:57.143
HOW DO YOU KNOW
SO MUCH ABOUT ALL OF THIS?

07:57.177 --> 07:58.311
Sam:
DANI, EVERYTHING OKAY?

07:58.345 --> 08:00.146
YES. I THINK.

08:00.180 --> 08:02.182
I -- OH.

08:02.215 --> 08:05.251
UM...SAM CONTE,
THIS IS NICO CARELES.

08:05.285 --> 08:07.020
THE SECURITY GUY
WHO KNOWS EVERYTHING, RIGHT?

08:08.188 --> 08:10.090
RIGHT.

08:17.997 --> 08:20.033
I'M SURE THAT WASN'T
ON ANYONE'S, UH,

08:20.066 --> 08:22.268
DAILY PLANNER, NOW,
WAS IT?

08:22.302 --> 08:25.205
LISTEN, I'M SURE WE'RE ALL
A BIT SHAKEN UP,

08:25.238 --> 08:27.007
BUT YOU DON'T LIVE
ON TOP OF THE MOUNTAIN

08:27.040 --> 08:29.676
WITHOUT SOMEONE
TRYING TO KNOCK YOU OFF.

08:29.709 --> 08:32.278
OUR ENEMIES ONLY WIN
IF WE LET THEM.

08:32.312 --> 08:34.714
ALSO, LET ME REMIND YOU
THAT THERE'S NO EVIDENCE

08:34.748 --> 08:36.349
OF ANY WRONGDOING AT V3.

08:36.383 --> 08:38.952
THERE'S NO EVIDENCE THAT V3
IS EVEN A TARGET

08:38.985 --> 08:41.287
OF ANY SORT OF INVESTIGATION.

08:41.321 --> 08:44.624
I PROMISE, WE WILL GET
TO THE BOTTOM OF THIS.

08:44.657 --> 08:49.029
SO, I SUGGEST WE JUST GO BACK
TO WORK, BUSINESS AS USUAL.

08:49.062 --> 08:51.164
OH, AND, UH...

08:51.197 --> 08:53.667
CONGRATULATIONS
ON OUR FIRST FBI RAID.

08:53.700 --> 08:56.036
LET'S GIVE OURSELVES ALL
A BIG ROUND OF APPLAUSE, HUH?

08:56.069 --> 08:58.138
[ APPLAUSE ]

09:03.176 --> 09:05.045
Troy: YOU GET THE WAR ROOM
UP AND RUNNING.

09:05.078 --> 09:05.979
YOU CALL EVERY CLIENT,

09:07.113 --> 09:08.114
EVERY COMPANY
THAT V3 IS IN BUSINESS WITH

09:09.049 --> 09:10.150
AND LET THEM KNOW
THAT WE ARE ROCK SOLID,

09:10.984 --> 09:11.885
AND WHOEVER
IS RESPONSIBLE FOR THIS,

09:11.918 --> 09:13.753
LET THEM KNOW
THERE WILL BE HELL TO PAY.

09:13.787 --> 09:14.521
OH, THANK YOU, JIMMY.

09:15.355 --> 09:15.989
I APPRECIATE ANYTHING
YOU CAN DO.

09:16.690 --> 09:17.323
ALL RIGHT, MY MAN.
THANKS.

09:17.357 --> 09:18.658
HEY.

09:18.692 --> 09:20.226
GET ME TONY
OVER AT JUSTICE.

09:20.260 --> 09:22.762
ALSO NELLY AND NIKKI FINK
AT DEADLINE.

09:22.796 --> 09:25.031
WE HAVE TO SPIN THIS
BEFORE IT GETS SPUN.

09:25.065 --> 09:27.067
HEY, UM, I KNOW THIS
MIGHT BE A BAD TIME.

09:27.100 --> 09:29.035
BAD TIME?
WHAT MAKES YOU SAY THAT?

09:29.069 --> 09:31.171
LISTEN, CONNOR,
I APPRECIATED YOUR SPEECH,

09:31.204 --> 09:32.772
BUT THIS IS NOT
BUSINESS AS USUAL.

09:32.806 --> 09:34.708
I HAVE BEEN APPROACHED
BY SEVERAL PEOPLE

09:34.741 --> 09:36.343
WHO ARE WORRIED
THEY'RE LOSING THEIR JOBS.

09:36.376 --> 09:38.678
SANTINO, I UNDERSTAND.
WE'RE UNDER SIEGE, OKAY?

09:38.712 --> 09:41.348
BUT I HAVE 100 EMPLOYEES
LOOKING AT ME FOR LEADERSHIP.

09:41.381 --> 09:43.683
I CAN'T PROJECT WEAKNESS
IN A TIME OF CRISIS.

09:43.717 --> 09:46.686
UNDERSTOOD, BUT DO YOU
ACTUALLY HAVE ANY IDEA

09:46.720 --> 09:47.687
WHAT'S GOING ON?

09:47.721 --> 09:48.988
NO. I DON'T.

09:50.023 --> 09:50.724
SO, UNTIL I DO, I WOULD LIKE YOU
TO DO DOUBLE DUTY

09:51.691 --> 09:52.292
AND TRY TO CALM THE MASSES
THE BEST YOU CAN.

09:53.326 --> 09:54.694
HELLO. THIS IS CONNOR McCLANE
FOR HARVEY LEVIN.

09:58.331 --> 10:01.334
BAM.

10:01.368 --> 10:02.802
THE FEDS JUST
RAID THE PLACE.

10:02.836 --> 10:04.371
HELL OF A STORY.

10:04.404 --> 10:06.106
IT'S A TRUE STORY.

10:06.139 --> 10:07.140
I MEAN, I'M TALKING
"UNTOUCHABLES."

10:07.173 --> 10:08.174
THEY WENT
FULL LOCK-DOWN.

10:09.109 --> 10:11.244
NO CELLPHONES, NO PDAs,
NO WHATEVER, OKAY?

10:11.277 --> 10:12.379
THAT'S WHY
I MISSED PRACTICE.

10:12.412 --> 10:13.713
YOU KNOW, YOU WANT TO
CHECK ON ME,

10:14.714 --> 10:15.648
YOU CALL THAT AGENCY DUDE.
HE'LL VOUCH FOR ME.

10:16.349 --> 10:18.385
HERE'S A QUESTION
FOR YOU.

10:18.418 --> 10:21.855
WHAT'S THE FINE
FOR BEING LATE TO PRACTICE?

10:21.888 --> 10:24.024
FIVE G's.

10:24.057 --> 10:26.259
CORRECT.
WHAT ARE THE EXCEPTIONS?

10:26.292 --> 10:28.128
DEATH AND ALIEN ABDUCTION.

10:28.161 --> 10:29.362
AND WHICH ONE HAPPENED
TO YOU?

10:29.396 --> 10:32.132
NOW THAT YOU MENTION IT,

10:32.165 --> 10:35.235
THE FBI GUYS DID LOOK
A LITTLE "MEN IN BLACK."

10:35.268 --> 10:39.039
YOU OWE ME 5K,
MR. KING.

10:41.074 --> 10:42.108
OKAY.

10:46.179 --> 10:48.415
AND JUST A LITTLE
HEADS UP.

10:48.448 --> 10:51.251
I'M SEQUESTERING THE TEAM
IN A HOTEL ROOM SATURDAY NIGHT.

10:51.284 --> 10:53.186
CURFEW -- 10:00 P.M.

10:53.219 --> 10:56.256
WAIT, I'M SORRY -- CURFEW
AND A HOTEL FOR A HOME GAME?

10:56.289 --> 10:58.792
AN IMPORTANT GAME.
NO DISTRACTIONS.

10:58.825 --> 10:59.893
YOU GOT A PROBLEM
WITH THAT?

10:59.926 --> 11:02.195
NO, NO PROBLEM
WITH THAT AT ALL.

11:02.228 --> 11:06.766
I WILL BE SNUG AS A BUG
IN A KING-SIZE BED AT 9:59.

11:06.800 --> 11:07.801
YEAH, YOU BETTER BE,

11:08.735 --> 11:09.135
'CAUSE I DON'T CARE
HOW MANY BALLS YOU CATCH

11:09.636 --> 11:10.704
OR T.D.s YOU MAKE,

11:11.805 --> 11:13.406
YOU SCREW UP AGAIN,
I WILL SHIP YOUR ASS TO BUFFALO

11:13.440 --> 11:15.308
AND GO RIGHT BACK TO MY DINNER
LIKE NOTHING HAPPENED.

11:15.342 --> 11:16.242
AM I CLEAR?

11:17.377 --> 11:19.112
CRYSTAL.

11:19.145 --> 11:21.147
NOW GET OUT OF HERE.

11:24.351 --> 11:26.252
YOU'RE SURE,
DR. SANTINO?

11:26.286 --> 11:26.986
YES, HAL.

11:27.954 --> 11:28.488
I'M SURE THE FBI's
NOT GONNA CARE

11:29.322 --> 11:30.190
WHAT YOU DO
IN THE EMPLOYEE KITCHEN,

11:31.224 --> 11:32.092
BUT I WOULD STOP STEALING
OTHER PEOPLE'S LUNCHES,

11:32.659 --> 11:32.992
JUST 'CAUSE.
OKAY.

11:34.227 --> 11:36.830
[ LAUGHS ]

11:36.863 --> 11:39.399
OH, UH, CARL, RIGHT?

11:39.432 --> 11:41.501
WE WEREN'T FORMALLY INTRODUCED,
BUT I'M DR. DANI SANTINO.

11:41.534 --> 11:42.836
I KNOW.

11:43.870 --> 11:44.804
DO YOU KNOW WHY HUMPTY DUMPTY
WAS A FOOLISH EGG?

11:44.838 --> 11:46.840
OH. NO. WHY?

11:46.873 --> 11:48.108
BECAUSE HE SHOULD
NEVER HAVE BEEN

11:48.141 --> 11:49.309
ON THE WALL
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

11:50.443 --> 11:51.444
IT WAS JUST A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE HE FELL AND CRACKED.

11:52.245 --> 11:54.214
I'M SORRY.
I'M NOT FOLLOWING YOU.

11:54.247 --> 11:55.515
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M S-- I'M SORRY.

11:55.548 --> 11:57.217
I, UM...

11:57.250 --> 11:58.818
I-I DON'T SLEEP
VERY WELL.

11:58.852 --> 12:01.521
MAYBE YOU CAN GIVE ME SOMETHING
TO HELP ME WITH SLEEPING.

12:01.554 --> 12:02.822
AH.

12:02.856 --> 12:04.190
I DON'T PRESCRIBE.

12:04.224 --> 12:06.826
YOU'D HAVE TO GO TO
A PSYCHIATRIST FOR THAT.

12:06.860 --> 12:08.128
YOU ALL RIGHT?

12:08.161 --> 12:09.929
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

12:09.963 --> 12:12.298
OH. EXCUSE ME.

12:15.535 --> 12:17.470
COULD WE TALK
PRIVATELY?

12:32.519 --> 12:34.421
I DON'T APPRECIATE
BEING BLINDSIDED.

12:38.425 --> 12:41.394
NEED I REMIND YOU,
YOU'RE AN INFORMANT --

12:41.428 --> 12:42.862
NOT AN AGENT.

12:42.896 --> 12:45.398
INFORMATION IS STRICTLY
ON A NEED-TO-KNOW BASIS.

12:45.432 --> 12:47.334
OH, SO YOU DIDN'T THINK
I NEEDED TO KNOW

12:47.367 --> 12:49.269
THAT V3 WAS GONNA
BE RAIDED?

12:49.302 --> 12:51.571
I WAS PRESERVING
YOUR COVER.

12:51.604 --> 12:53.306
THANKS FOR THE ASSIST,
BUT I'M GOOD.

12:53.340 --> 12:56.343
THIS ISN'T
YOUR INVESTIGATION.

12:56.376 --> 12:58.445
JUST SIT TIGHT.
WAIT FOR THE INSTRUCTIONS.

12:58.478 --> 12:59.312
THAT'S ALL YOU NEED
TO WORRY ABOUT.

13:00.347 --> 13:03.283
I'VE GIVEN YOU GUYS
OVER SIX MONTHS OF MY LIFE,

13:03.316 --> 13:05.318
AND I'M READY FOR IT
TO BE OVER, QUICKLY,

13:05.352 --> 13:06.553
SO I CAN PACK MY BAGS
AND GO TO DALLAS,

13:06.586 --> 13:08.288
WHERE A VERY LUCRATIVE JOB
WAS WAITING FOR ME

13:08.321 --> 13:10.590
UNTIL I WAS
RUDELY INTERRUPTED.

13:10.623 --> 13:12.325
THE MORE YOU KEEP ME
IN THE DARK,

13:12.359 --> 13:13.960
THE LESS HELP
I CAN BE TO YOU,

13:13.993 --> 13:15.995
AND THE LONGER
THIS WHOLE THING TAKES.

13:16.029 --> 13:18.898
IT'S NOT YOUR CALL.

13:18.932 --> 13:23.503
BESIDES, I'D HATE TO SEE
YOUR FRIEND DR. SANTINO

13:23.536 --> 13:26.206
GET MIXED UP IN THIS
ANY MORE THAN SHE ALREADY IS.

13:26.239 --> 13:27.540
YEAH.

13:27.574 --> 13:31.211
DR. SANTINO
IS A VERY NICE LADY.

13:31.244 --> 13:32.479
WE CAN ALL AGREE
ON THAT.

13:32.512 --> 13:34.981
BUT IN FOUR WEEKS' TIME,

13:35.015 --> 13:37.317
I'M GOING AWOL
ON THIS OPERATION.

13:37.350 --> 13:39.319
IT'LL BE LIKE
I NEVER EXISTED.

13:39.352 --> 13:40.320
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

13:42.455 --> 13:45.358
YOU GOT FOUR WEEKS
TO FIGURE IT OUT.

13:46.493 --> 13:48.628
ENJOY YOUR MEAL.

13:53.566 --> 13:55.502
<i>...SENT SHOCK WAVES</i>
<i>THROUGH THE SPORTS</i>

13:55.535 --> 13:57.437
<i>AND ENTERTAINMENT</i>
<i>INDUSTRIES TODAY</i>

13:57.470 --> 14:00.240
<i>AS THE FBI ISSUED</i>
<i>A COURT-ORDERED SEARCH WARRANT</i>

14:00.273 --> 14:02.542
<i>IN WHAT APPEARS TO BE</i>
<i>AN ONGOING INVESTIGATION.</i>

14:02.575 --> 14:05.578
<i>WHAT THAT INVESTIGATION IS</i>
<i>IS ANYONE'S GUESS.</i>

14:05.612 --> 14:08.948
<i>V3 C.E.O. CONNOR McCLANE</i>
<i>HAD THIS TO SAY</i>

14:08.982 --> 14:11.451
<i>WHEN HE SPOKE WITH REPORTERS</i>
<i>EARLIER TODAY.</i>

14:11.484 --> 14:12.919
<i>LOOK, THERE'S NO EVIDENCE</i>
<i>THAT WE'RE THE TARGET</i>

14:12.952 --> 14:14.554
<i>OF ANY SORT OF INVESTIGATION.</i>

14:14.587 --> 14:16.356
<i>V3 HAS NOTHING TO HIDE.</i>

14:16.389 --> 14:18.058
<i>WE WERE FULLY COOPERATIVE</i>
<i>WITH THE FBI,</i>

14:18.091 --> 14:19.526
<i>SO IT'S BACK</i>
<i>TO BUSINESS AS USUAL.</i>

14:21.594 --> 14:24.698
SO, OUR $1,000-AN-HOUR
LEGAL TEAM

14:24.731 --> 14:26.266
IS AS MUCH IN THE DARK
AS WE ARE.

14:26.299 --> 14:27.500
MM-HMM.

14:27.534 --> 14:29.069
AND UNTIL INDICTMENTS
ARE HANDLED DOWN,

14:29.102 --> 14:32.038
WE HAVE NO IDEA WHO OR WHAT
IT IS THEY'RE INVESTIGATING.

14:32.072 --> 14:33.273
COULD BE MONTHS.

14:34.174 --> 14:35.475
THE FBI MUST THINK
THEY GOT A DAMN GOOD CASE

14:35.508 --> 14:36.609
TO COME IN
FULL FORCE LIKE THAT.

14:37.610 --> 14:38.445
THERE'S NOTHING IN OUR FILES
I'M WORRIED ABOUT.

14:39.412 --> 14:40.013
THE IRS HAS BEEN THROUGH
EVERY PIECE OF PAPER

14:40.780 --> 14:42.615
IN THIS OFFICE
100 TIMES OVER.

14:42.649 --> 14:45.952
I'M MORE CONCERNED WITH THE RAT
WHO'S TRYING TO SINK OUR SHIP.

14:45.985 --> 14:47.554
THE ATTORNEYS SAID

14:47.587 --> 14:49.422
THAT THE FEDS
WOULDN'T COME IN LIKE THAT

14:49.456 --> 14:50.523
UNLESS THEY HAD
ONE MORE SOURCE,

14:51.491 --> 14:55.028
SO THERE MUST BE
ONE OTHER HAND AT PLAY HERE.

14:55.061 --> 14:56.629
THE ONLY TWO PEOPLE
WHO ARE<i>NOT</i>SUSPECTS

14:56.663 --> 14:58.398
ARE IN THIS OFFICE.

14:58.431 --> 15:00.567
LEAVE NO STONE UNTURNED.

15:00.600 --> 15:04.070
WE HAVE TO FIND OUT WHO'S
TRYING TO TAKE US DOWN.

15:09.576 --> 15:12.512
AND WE ARE GOING TO MAKE JULIO
A ONE-NAME BRAND.

15:12.545 --> 15:13.113
REALLY?
MM-HMM.

15:13.146 --> 15:15.448
LIKE LEBRON?
LIKE TIGER?

15:15.482 --> 15:17.183
LIKE BECKHAM AND...

15:17.217 --> 15:18.385
OBAMA.

15:18.418 --> 15:20.487
I LOVE IT, BRUCE.
YOU'RE GOOD.

15:20.520 --> 15:22.255
SHE IS GOOD. TRUST ME.
I'VE BEEN THERE.

15:22.288 --> 15:23.556
SHE IS GOOD.

15:23.590 --> 15:25.392
CONNOR McCLANE, HOW THE HELL
ARE YOU, MAN?

15:25.425 --> 15:28.028
JULIO JONES.
YOU ARE A SUPERSTAR.

15:28.061 --> 15:28.695
HOW ARE THE FALCONS
TREATING YOU?

15:28.728 --> 15:29.596
THEY'RE TREATING ME
FINE,

15:30.397 --> 15:31.197
BUT NOT AS FINE
AS MS. BRUCE HERE.

15:32.298 --> 15:33.166
MM. YOU KNOW, WE'RE RIGHT
IN THE MIDDLE OF A MEETING.

15:34.200 --> 15:35.101
YEAH?
ACTUALLY, WE WERE
JUST FINISHING UP.

15:36.002 --> 15:36.469
I GOT ANOTHER MEETING
I GOT TO GET TO.

15:37.203 --> 15:38.038
OKAY.
SO, WE'LL TALK LATER.

15:38.605 --> 15:39.406
ALL RIGHT.
HI, BRUCE.

15:41.207 --> 15:43.109
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

15:43.143 --> 15:45.545
WELL, YOU LOOK LIKE
YOU COULD USE SOME COMPANY.

15:45.578 --> 15:47.447
WELL, YOU LOOK LIKE
YOU COULD USE A GOOD LAWYER.

15:47.480 --> 15:50.050
I SAW YOU ON TV
LAST NIGHT, CONNOR.

15:50.083 --> 15:51.051
IF YOU WERE SPINNING
ANY HARDER,

15:51.985 --> 15:53.420
YOU'D HAVE YOUR OWN
GRAVITATIONAL PULL.

15:53.453 --> 15:55.555
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

15:55.588 --> 15:57.557
WHAT DO<i>YOU</i>WANT?

15:57.590 --> 15:59.359
WHEN SOMETHING'S WRONG
IN YOUR HOUSE,

15:59.392 --> 16:01.561
WHY IS YOUR FIRST INSTINCT
TO LOOK INSIDE MINE?

16:01.594 --> 16:03.263
'CAUSE YOU FIGHT DIRTY.

16:03.296 --> 16:05.198
HOW'D YOU GET THE FEDS
TO COME CHECK ME OUT?

16:05.231 --> 16:07.434
[ Laughing ] ARE YOU SERIOUSLY
ACCUSING ME OF SETTING YOU UP?

16:07.467 --> 16:09.302
YEAH.
WHY WOULD I DO THAT?

16:09.336 --> 16:11.638
OH, I DON'T KNOW, MAYBE BECAUSE
I DIDN'T MAKE YOU PARTNER.

16:13.273 --> 16:15.475
WELL, YOU GIVE ME
A LOT OF CREDIT.

16:15.508 --> 16:17.177
NO, I'M GIVING YOU
ALL THE CREDIT.

16:17.210 --> 16:18.378
IN FACT, Y-YOU'VE BEEN
TRYING TO SCREW ME

16:18.411 --> 16:20.113
SINCE THE DAY
YOU LEFT V3.

16:20.146 --> 16:21.214
AND YOU'RE NOT
TRYING TO SCREW ME?

16:21.247 --> 16:22.515
NO. I HAVE A NEW HOBBY.

16:22.549 --> 16:24.517
REALLY?
WHAT'S HER NAME?

16:24.551 --> 16:25.685
[ LAUGHS ]
THAT'S GOOD.

16:25.719 --> 16:27.587
BY THE WAY,
GREAT BOOB JOB.

16:27.620 --> 16:29.089
YOU MIGHT WANT TO TELL
THE RIGHT ONE

16:29.856 --> 16:31.191
THAT THE LEFT ONE'S
ABOUT THREE INCHES HIGHER.

16:31.224 --> 16:32.192
THREE INCHES?
MM-HMM.

16:32.225 --> 16:35.128
WELL, THERE'S SOMETHING
YOU'D KNOW A LOT ABOUT.

16:35.161 --> 16:38.131
WE BOTH KNOW THAT THAT'S ONLY
ABOUT 1/3 OF THE STORY.

16:38.164 --> 16:40.200
OKAY. IS THERE A POINT
TO THIS LITTLE VISIT?

16:40.233 --> 16:41.735
YEAH. THERE IS A POINT
TO THIS LITTLE VISIT.

16:41.768 --> 16:44.104
YOU HAD ACCESS
TO A LOT OF INFORMATION,

16:44.137 --> 16:45.472
SO IF ANY OF IT GETS OUT,

16:45.505 --> 16:47.540
I'M GONNA KNOW
IT'S YOU, BRUCE.

16:47.574 --> 16:50.643
SO, IF YOU THREW ANY SAND,
PREPARE TO GET DIRTY.

16:54.314 --> 16:55.582
[ SCOFFS ]

16:57.250 --> 17:01.254
ASSETS AND LIABILITIES,
DEBITS AND CREDITS --

17:01.287 --> 17:02.489
THESE ARE ALL ITEMS
I KNOW WHERE THEY BELONG

17:02.522 --> 17:03.623
ON THE BALANCE SHEET,

17:03.656 --> 17:07.127
HOW TO MAKE THEM ALL
RECONCILE.

17:07.160 --> 17:09.262
SO WHAT'S THROWING YOU
OFF BALANCE NOW?

17:09.295 --> 17:13.166
I'M, UH, I'M GOING THROUGH
A MESSY DIVORCE.

17:13.199 --> 17:17.303
AND MY WIFE, JULIA,
SHE WILL TAKE THIS FBI RAID

17:17.337 --> 17:20.507
AND USE IT AGAINST ME
SOMEHOW.

17:20.540 --> 17:22.342
DO YOU HAVE ANY CHILDREN?

17:22.375 --> 17:23.543
GROWN.

17:23.576 --> 17:26.646
MY SON
IS A CONCERT VIOLINIST.

17:26.680 --> 17:28.248
MY DAUGHTER,
SHE'S GOING TO YALE.

17:28.281 --> 17:30.150
WOW.

17:30.183 --> 17:31.685
I GAVE THEM EVERYTHING.

17:36.256 --> 17:40.360
JULIA, SHE, UM...

17:40.393 --> 17:43.797
SHE WANTED ME TO QUIT THIS JOB
AT V3 FIVE YEARS AGO --

17:43.830 --> 17:45.732
SAID SHE THOUGHT
IT WAS KILLING ME.

17:45.765 --> 17:47.267
HOW SO?

17:47.300 --> 17:49.602
THE SLEEPING --
LACK THEREOF.

17:49.636 --> 17:51.538
SO, IT'S BEEN GOING ON
FOR SOME TIME, THEN --

17:51.571 --> 17:52.706
THE SLEEP ISSUES?

17:52.739 --> 17:54.274
YEAH.

17:54.307 --> 17:57.777
WELL, INSOMNIA OFTEN
HAS AN UNDERLYING CAUSE,

17:57.811 --> 18:00.547
LIKE STRESS
OR EMOTIONAL UPHEAVAL,

18:00.580 --> 18:02.182
DEPRESSION.

18:04.384 --> 18:06.286
BUT YOU DIDN'T COME HERE

18:06.319 --> 18:10.523
TO TALK ABOUT YOUR DIVORCE
OR YOUR SLEEP PROBLEMS.

18:10.557 --> 18:14.227
THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE
GOING ON, RIGHT?

18:18.398 --> 18:20.600
EVERYTHING
THAT I SAY TO YOU

18:20.633 --> 18:23.670
IS CONFIDENTIAL, RIGHT?

18:23.703 --> 18:27.207
UNLESS YOU PLAN ON HARMING
YOURSELF OR SOMEONE ELSE.

18:32.412 --> 18:35.382
I'M THE ONE
THE FBI IS LOOKING FOR.

18:36.549 --> 18:38.451
Sheera: SURPRISE.

18:38.485 --> 18:40.320
[ T.K. LAUGHS ]

18:40.353 --> 18:41.354
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

18:41.388 --> 18:43.423
I HAD MATCHING ONES
MADE FOR US.

18:43.456 --> 18:44.657
YES, YOU DID.

18:44.691 --> 18:46.326
[ LAUGHS ]

18:46.359 --> 18:48.328
OH, THIS MUST HAVE COST YOU
A FORTUNE, BABE.

18:48.361 --> 18:50.630
WELL, SHE-K NEEDS TO MAKE
A SPLASHY DEBUT

18:50.663 --> 18:52.565
AT THE SATURDAY
V3 CHARITY EXTRAVAGANZA.

18:52.599 --> 18:54.267
SO...

18:54.300 --> 18:55.335
OKAY, UH, FIRST OF ALL,
"SHE-KAY,"

18:55.368 --> 18:56.870
AND THAT'S THIS SATURDAY?

18:56.903 --> 18:57.871
UH, YEAH.

18:57.904 --> 19:00.240
YEAH, I-I-I CAN'T GO.

19:00.273 --> 19:01.241
WHAT?

19:01.274 --> 19:03.343
NO. THAT'S NOT AN OPTION.

19:03.376 --> 19:05.612
THIS IS THE BEGINNING
OF OUR "HELLO, WORLD" TOUR.

19:05.645 --> 19:07.414
ALSO, IT'S CONNOR'S BABY.

19:07.447 --> 19:09.349
IT IS REALLY BAD FORM
TO BLOW THIS OFF.

19:09.382 --> 19:11.484
YEAH, WELL,
MY CRAZY-ASS COACH

19:11.518 --> 19:13.753
HAS THE ENTIRE TEAM
SEQUESTERED IN A HOTEL...
UH-HUH.

19:13.787 --> 19:16.489
...WITH A MANDATORY CURFEW
OF 10:00 P.M., OKAY?

19:16.523 --> 19:18.491
SO, IT'S EVEN WORSE FORM
FOR ME TO BLOW THAT OFF.

19:18.525 --> 19:20.460
10:00 P.M.? NO SWEAT.

19:20.493 --> 19:22.729
WE'LL ARRIVE AT 8:00,
WE WILL WORK THE RED CARPET,

19:22.762 --> 19:25.832
WE'LL GET THOSE FABULOUS PHOTOS,
AND THEN WE'LL SNEAK OUT.

19:25.865 --> 19:27.400
T.K.,
THIS IS A NO-BRAINER.

19:27.434 --> 19:28.501
[ Chuckling ] YEAH.

19:28.535 --> 19:29.736
AS IN, "YOU MUST HAVE
NO BRAINS

19:29.769 --> 19:31.304
IF YOU THINK THAT PLAN
IS GONNA WORK."

19:31.338 --> 19:32.272
WHAT?

19:32.305 --> 19:33.840
V3 IN THE CITY.
YEAH.

19:33.873 --> 19:36.376
HOTEL, LONG ISLAND.
GOT THAT.

19:36.409 --> 19:38.645
OKAY, IN BETWEEN ALL THAT
IS NEW YORK CITY TRAFFIC --

19:38.678 --> 19:39.779
SATURDAY NIGHT.

19:39.813 --> 19:42.515
[ LAUGHS ]
NIGHTMARE, OKAY?

19:42.549 --> 19:43.850
LOT OF HOLES
IN YOUR NO-BRAINER.

19:43.883 --> 19:45.385
T.K...

19:45.418 --> 19:47.587
THESE...

19:47.620 --> 19:51.524
ARE THE KEYS
TO OUR FUTURE.

19:51.558 --> 19:53.626
[ SIGHS ]

19:53.660 --> 19:55.528
SO CAN YOU PLEASE
TRUST ME?

19:55.562 --> 19:57.330
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:59.699 --> 20:01.735
WELL,
YOU ARE JUST A...

20:01.768 --> 20:03.870
CAN-DO
TYPE OF GIRL, HUH?

20:03.903 --> 20:06.639
YEAH, I AM A
CAN-DO-ALL-KINDS-OF-THINGS GIRL.

20:06.673 --> 20:09.776
[ LAUGHS ]

20:09.809 --> 20:11.745
I MIGHT HAVE JUST GOT MYSELF
INTO A SITUATION,

20:11.778 --> 20:13.813
AND I DON'T SEE A WAY OUT.

20:13.847 --> 20:15.315
COULD WE TALK
TO A LAWYER?

20:15.348 --> 20:18.551
IF MY WIFE AND KIDS
FOUND OUT...

20:18.585 --> 20:20.320
JESUS.

20:21.955 --> 20:23.857
ARE THERE OTHERS
INVOLVED AT V3?

20:26.526 --> 20:29.596
LOOK, I AM ONLY HERE
TO TALK ABOUT ME, OKAY?

20:29.629 --> 20:31.431
OKAY.

20:31.464 --> 20:34.668
OKAY. SO, THEN,
LET'S REVIEW YOUR OPTIONS.

20:35.935 --> 20:37.737
WELL [CHUCKLES]
THERE ARE NONE --

20:37.771 --> 20:38.738
I MEAN,
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

20:38.772 --> 20:40.907
THERE ARE
ALWAYS OPTIONS,

20:40.940 --> 20:43.376
AND WE'RE GONNA FIGURE OUT
THE BEST ONE FOR YOU.

20:43.410 --> 20:45.845
OKAY, WELL,
OPTION NUMBER ONE

20:45.879 --> 20:48.448
IS THAT I CONFESS
TO THE FBI,

20:48.481 --> 20:51.718
THAT I BRING INCREDIBLE SHAME
ON THE FAMILY,

20:51.751 --> 20:54.721
AND, UH, I GO TO JAIL.

20:54.754 --> 20:55.922
THAT SOUNDS FUN.

20:55.955 --> 20:59.659
OPTION TWO IS THAT
I FLEE THE COUNTRY.

20:59.693 --> 21:02.462
AND THEN YOU'RE
GOING TO BE RUNNING

21:02.495 --> 21:04.564
AND CONSTANTLY
LOOKING OVER YOUR SHOULDER.

21:04.597 --> 21:07.400
OPTION THREE IS THAT I JUST
HOLD TIGHT AND THAT, YOU KNOW,

21:07.434 --> 21:08.635
I JUST HOPE THE WHOLE THING
BLOWS OVER,

21:08.668 --> 21:10.370
WHICH IS UNLIKELY.

21:15.642 --> 21:18.611
[ SIGHS ]

21:18.645 --> 21:22.515
OKAY. I, UM...

21:22.549 --> 21:24.651
I-I THINK I KNOW WHAT OPTION
I WANT TO CHOOSE.

21:27.520 --> 21:29.456
WILL YOU HELP ME?

21:29.489 --> 21:31.791
YES.

21:33.660 --> 21:34.961
MORNING.

21:34.994 --> 21:36.463
GOOD AFTERNOON.

21:36.496 --> 21:37.397
DID YOU HAVE
AN EARLY LUNCH?

21:37.430 --> 21:39.566
I DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING
ON THE BOOKS FOR YOU.

21:39.599 --> 21:41.401
NO, I HAD AN APPOINTMENT.

21:41.434 --> 21:42.936
ANY MESSAGES?
A FEW.

21:42.969 --> 21:45.538
SAM CALLED, CONFIRMING
YOUR DINNER FOR TONIGHT.

21:45.572 --> 21:46.740
OH. OKAY.
CAN YOU --

21:46.773 --> 21:48.641
7:00 AT RUBIKS,
UPPER WEST.

21:48.675 --> 21:49.809
OH. THANK YOU.

21:51.611 --> 21:53.513
HELLO, DOCTOR.

21:53.546 --> 21:54.881
PALOMA.
TROY.

21:58.685 --> 21:59.619
OKAY.

21:59.652 --> 22:00.920
[ SIGHS ]

22:00.954 --> 22:02.489
I JUST THOUGHT
I'D CHECK IN WITH YOU.

22:03.757 --> 22:05.558
SEE HOW THE MASSES
ARE HOLDING UP.

22:05.592 --> 22:07.827
THEY'RE OKAY,
CONSIDERING.

22:07.861 --> 22:09.729
I IMAGINE THIS
HAS TO BE A, UH...

22:09.763 --> 22:13.533
UNSETTLING TIME FOR EVERYONE,
SOME MORE THAN OTHERS.

22:13.566 --> 22:15.068
IS THERE ANYONE
IN PARTICULAR

22:15.101 --> 22:16.736
THAT WE SHOULD BE
CONCERNED ABOUT?

22:18.571 --> 22:21.675
TROY...

22:21.708 --> 22:25.045
LET ME REMIND YOU AGAIN
THAT I'M A THERAPIST.

22:25.078 --> 22:26.479
WHETHER I WORK
IN A CORPORATION

22:27.213 --> 22:27.981
OR HANG A SHINGLE OUT
ON A STREET CORNER,

22:28.915 --> 22:29.949
WHEN MY CLIENTS
TALK TO ME CONFIDENTIALLY,

22:29.983 --> 22:32.819
I PROTECT THEIR PRIVACY.

22:32.852 --> 22:34.788
OF COURSE YOU DO.

22:34.821 --> 22:35.989
I'D EXPECT NOTHING LESS.

22:38.825 --> 22:41.027
WELL, I'LL LEAVE YOU
TO IT.

23:00.613 --> 23:02.716
SEEMS LIKE OLD TIMES.

23:02.749 --> 23:04.117
WHAT'S UP, DOC?

23:04.150 --> 23:05.785
[ SIGHS ]

23:05.819 --> 23:09.022
I KNOW WHY
THE FBI RAIDED V3.

23:11.491 --> 23:13.893
I'M LISTENING.

23:13.927 --> 23:16.863
SOMEONE CAME TO ME.

23:16.896 --> 23:20.000
A V3 EMPLOYEE --
CAN'T GIVE A NAME.

23:20.033 --> 23:21.735
[ SIGHS ]

23:21.768 --> 23:24.070
BUT LET'S SAY THIS PERSON
WANTED TO TELL THEIR STORY

23:24.104 --> 23:28.041
TO THE FBI --
ADMIT THEIR GUILT.

23:28.074 --> 23:30.643
IS THERE ANY CHANCE
FOR LENIENCY?

23:30.677 --> 23:31.945
DEPENDS.

23:31.978 --> 23:33.880
ON?
THE CRIME --

23:33.913 --> 23:35.849
WHAT LAWS WERE BROKEN,

23:35.882 --> 23:37.784
HOW MANY PEOPLE
WERE INVOLVED,

23:37.817 --> 23:40.920
HOW MUCH MONEY,
WHO WAS HURT.

23:40.954 --> 23:42.055
WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME?

23:43.757 --> 23:45.025
NOTHING.

23:45.058 --> 23:48.561
[ SIGHS ]

23:48.595 --> 23:51.631
I CAN SET UP A MEETING...

23:51.664 --> 23:53.700
WITH SOMEONE I KNOW
FROM MY TIME AT THE BUREAU.

23:55.902 --> 23:57.704
YOU WORKED AT THE FBI?

23:57.737 --> 23:59.673
BRIEFLY.

24:01.675 --> 24:03.710
THE ONION PEELS
SO SLOWLY.

24:03.743 --> 24:05.845
MM.

24:07.647 --> 24:09.783
WELL, I WOULD APPRECIATE IT
IF YOU COULD SET THAT UP

24:09.816 --> 24:11.718
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE, OKAY?

24:21.895 --> 24:23.663
BURNING
THE MIDNIGHT OIL?

24:23.697 --> 24:25.732
JUST CATCHING UP
ON MY READING AND FILING.

24:25.765 --> 24:27.867
I LIKE TO STAY CURRENT
ON ALL THE V3 NEWS,

24:27.901 --> 24:30.203
ESPECIALLY WHEN IT'S
IN THE NATIONAL HEADLINES.

24:30.236 --> 24:33.673
I MUST SAY,
I ADMIRE YOUR TENACITY

24:33.707 --> 24:35.041
TO BE A V3 AGENT.

24:35.075 --> 24:36.743
I'M GLAD I CAUGHT
YOUR ATTENTION.

24:36.776 --> 24:39.979
NOT EVERYBODY HAS
YOUR DRIVE, AMBITION.

24:40.013 --> 24:41.748
ESPECIALLY AFTER HOURS.

24:41.781 --> 24:44.084
WELL, ISN'T THAT
HOW CONNOR NOTICED BRUCE?

24:44.117 --> 24:45.985
AFTER HOURS?
[ LAUGHS ]

24:46.019 --> 24:47.887
YOU DO KEEP UP
ON ALL THE NEWS.

24:47.921 --> 24:50.657
PAST IS PROLOGUE,
AS THEY SAY.

24:50.690 --> 24:51.858
THAT'S SHAKESPEARE --
"THE TEMPEST."

24:51.891 --> 24:53.660
ODDLY APPROPRIATE,

24:53.693 --> 24:55.962
THOUGH I AM PARTIAL TO
"THE MERCHANT OF VENICE."

24:55.995 --> 24:57.697
ARE YOU PARTIAL TO GETTING
ON THE FAST TRACK?

24:57.731 --> 24:59.833
DEPENDS ON WHAT
YOU HAVE IN MIND.

24:59.866 --> 25:01.634
HOW ABOUT
WE GO TO MY OFFICE

25:01.668 --> 25:03.203
AND DISCUSS
WHAT I HAVE IN MIND?

25:05.872 --> 25:07.140
LEAD THE WAY.

25:19.686 --> 25:21.087
HEY, CARL.

25:21.121 --> 25:22.322
HOW YOU HOLDING UP?

25:24.657 --> 25:25.692
OKAY.

25:27.360 --> 25:29.029
HAVE A GOOD NIGHT.

25:36.803 --> 25:39.272
CONNOR IS A GREAT MENTOR.

25:39.305 --> 25:40.206
HE HELPED ME MAKE THE SWITCH,

25:40.240 --> 25:42.809
AND I'D -- I'D TAKE
A BULLET FOR THE GUY.

25:42.842 --> 25:44.778
YEAH, A LOT OF PEOPLE
FEEL THAT WAY.

25:44.811 --> 25:46.613
THEY SHOW A REAL SENSE
OF LOYALTY.
MM.

25:48.114 --> 25:49.315
HE FOSTERS IT.

25:49.349 --> 25:51.117
TROY,
ON THE OTHER HAND --

25:51.151 --> 25:52.385
OH, MY GOD.

25:52.419 --> 25:54.187
WHAT IS THE DEAL
WITH THOSE TWO?

25:54.220 --> 25:55.188
WELL, LET'S FACE IT.

25:56.056 --> 25:56.756
EVERY GUY NEEDS
A HATCHET MAN, RIGHT?

25:57.757 --> 25:59.125
WELL, TROY CERTAINLY
LEADS WITH HIS HATCHET.

25:59.159 --> 26:00.393
I JUST TRY TO STAY
UNDER HIS RADAR,

26:00.427 --> 26:02.162
AND YOU SHOULD, TOO,

26:02.195 --> 26:04.097
ESPECIALLY WITH ALL THIS
FBI STUFF GOING ON.

26:04.130 --> 26:06.066
YEAH.

26:06.099 --> 26:07.801
DIDN'T THAT FREAK YOU OUT
AT ALL?

26:07.834 --> 26:09.135
NO.

26:09.169 --> 26:10.837
MY HANDS ARE CLEAN.

26:10.870 --> 26:13.740
WELL, MOSTLY.
I AM AN AGENT, AFTER ALL.

26:15.375 --> 26:17.377
TELL YOU WHAT -- SOMEBODY
HAS SOMETHING TO HIDE, THOUGH,

26:17.410 --> 26:18.712
THAT'S FOR SURE.

26:21.047 --> 26:25.352
YOU KNOW, NO MORE TALK
ABOUT WORK.

26:25.385 --> 26:27.420
YOU HAVE TROUBLE SEPARATING
WORK AND PLAY, DON'T YOU?

26:27.454 --> 26:30.123
OH, YOU KNOW,
JUST A LITTLE BIT.

26:30.156 --> 26:32.392
WELL, I CAN PROBABLY
HELP YOU WITH THAT.

26:39.432 --> 26:41.735
WHAT -- WHAT'S WRONG?

26:41.768 --> 26:44.270
I CAN HEAR YOU THINKING.

26:44.304 --> 26:45.372
OH.

26:45.405 --> 26:46.706
OH.

26:46.740 --> 26:48.908
I'M SORRY. I --

26:48.942 --> 26:51.177
I'M JUST -- I'M NOT
USED TO THE WHOLE...

26:51.211 --> 26:54.280
CASUAL, FLINGY THINGY.

26:54.314 --> 26:56.249
LOOK, I LIKE YOU.

26:56.282 --> 26:58.818
AND YOU SEEM
TO LIKE ME.

26:58.852 --> 27:01.855
AND WE ARE JUST TWO
CONSENTING ADULTS HAVING FUN.

27:01.888 --> 27:04.224
NOTHING WRONG WITH THAT.
YEAH. NO.

27:04.257 --> 27:06.793
BUT WHEN I TURN 40,
THAT'S A DIFFERENT STORY.

27:06.826 --> 27:08.895
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN
WHEN YOU TURN 40?

27:08.928 --> 27:12.399
I PROMISED MYSELF I WOULD
SETTLE DOWN AND GET SERIOUS.

27:12.432 --> 27:16.469
LUCKILY FOR YOU,
I STILL HAVE TWO YEARS LEFT.

27:16.503 --> 27:18.271
OH.

27:18.304 --> 27:19.372
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

27:21.775 --> 27:22.742
DON'T MOVE.

27:32.285 --> 27:34.854
EVERYTHING OKAY?

27:34.888 --> 27:36.222
IT'S A CLIENT.

27:36.256 --> 27:38.825
UM...

27:38.858 --> 27:40.226
GO.

27:40.260 --> 27:41.361
YEAH, GO. GO.

27:41.394 --> 27:43.730
RAIN CHECK.

27:43.763 --> 27:45.398
I STILL GOT
TWO GOOD YEARS LEFT, RIGHT?

27:51.838 --> 27:55.875
* STRANGELY CALM

27:55.909 --> 27:57.344
I CAN'T GO THROUGH
WITH THIS.

27:57.377 --> 27:58.345
WHY? WHAT HAPPENED?

27:58.378 --> 28:00.280
WHAT HAPPENED IS THAT
CONNOR McCLANE TRUSTED ME.

28:00.313 --> 28:01.881
HE GAVE ME MY CAREER.

28:01.915 --> 28:04.351
HE MADE ME A WEALTHY MAN,
AND -- AND I BETRAYED HIM.

28:04.384 --> 28:05.919
YOU STOLE MONEY
FROM THE COMPANY,

28:05.952 --> 28:07.954
BUT NOW YOU'RE GONNA
MAKE AMENDS, CARL.

28:07.987 --> 28:10.757
YEAH, I-I-I DON'T KNOW
IF THAT'S POSSIBLE.

28:11.958 --> 28:14.361
YOU HAVEN'T TOLD ME
EVERYTHING, HAVE YOU?

28:14.394 --> 28:15.895
LOOK, YOUR -- YOUR FRIEND

28:15.929 --> 28:18.431
WHO SET UP THIS MEETING
WITH THE FBI,

28:18.465 --> 28:20.800
HE DID IT FOR ME
TO MAKE A DEAL, RIGHT?
YES.

28:20.834 --> 28:22.769
AND YOU TRUST HIM?
YES.

28:22.802 --> 28:24.371
DO YOU WANT TO FREE YOURSELF
FROM THIS MESS,

28:24.404 --> 28:25.405
WHATEVER IT IS?

28:25.438 --> 28:26.873
I DO.

28:26.906 --> 28:29.175
I DO, FOR MY FAMILY,
FOR -- FOR MY SANITY.

28:29.209 --> 28:31.277
OKAY -- THEN WE'RE GONNA
MEET HERE TOMORROW

28:31.311 --> 28:33.013
WITH YOUR ATTORNEY,
AS PLANNED.

28:33.046 --> 28:34.914
CARL...

28:34.948 --> 28:38.785
THE TRUTH IS ALWAYS
THE BEST OPTION.

28:38.818 --> 28:41.187
[ SIGHS ] I SURE HOPE
YOU'RE RIGHT.

28:48.361 --> 28:50.864
FANCY MEETING YOU HERE.

28:50.897 --> 28:52.232
DO YOU HAVE
WHAT I ASKED FOR?

28:54.601 --> 28:57.937
THIS IS REALLY GOING TO HELP
THE INVESTIGATION?

28:57.971 --> 29:00.807
THE COMPANY THAT YOU LOVE
AND I LOVE,

29:00.840 --> 29:03.276
SOMEONE IS TRYING
TO TAKE IT DOWN.

29:03.309 --> 29:05.445
AND THAT DOESN'T BODE WELL
FOR EITHER OF OUR FUTURES.

29:10.517 --> 29:12.285
DANI'S SCHEDULE
IS ALL THERE,

29:12.318 --> 29:14.587
BUT THERE ARE THINGS THAT
SHE DOESN'T PUT ON THERE.

29:14.621 --> 29:15.822
LIKE?

29:15.855 --> 29:17.290
I DON'T KNOW.

29:17.323 --> 29:18.992
APPOINTMENTS
OUT OF THE OFFICE.

29:19.025 --> 29:20.393
OKAY.

29:20.427 --> 29:22.395
WELL, WHEN YOU DO KNOW,

29:22.429 --> 29:24.230
THERE'LL BE SOMETHING
WAITING FOR YOU.

29:24.264 --> 29:25.999
GOLD STAR?

29:26.032 --> 29:28.368
A RISING STAR.

29:45.618 --> 29:46.986
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

29:52.525 --> 29:54.294
GOOD NIGHT.

29:54.327 --> 29:56.329
GOOD NIGHT.

29:56.363 --> 29:57.997
Connor: WELL...

29:58.031 --> 29:59.599
THAT WAS AN INTERESTING
DEVELOPMENT.

29:59.632 --> 30:02.502
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

30:02.535 --> 30:04.537
WE'RE IN THE MIDDLE
OF A WAR HERE, CONNOR.

30:04.571 --> 30:06.306
A WAR THAT YOU STARTED.

30:06.339 --> 30:08.108
YOU SCREWED BRUCE
AND THEN SCREWED HER OVER,

30:08.141 --> 30:10.310
AND SHE'S DETERMINED
TO TAKE US DOWN.

30:10.343 --> 30:12.312
AND IT'S CLEAR, TO ME,

30:12.345 --> 30:14.547
THAT SHE'S GETTING HELP
FROM SOMEONE ON THE INSIDE.

30:14.581 --> 30:16.516
YOU KNOW,
WE DON'T KNOW WHO,

30:16.549 --> 30:18.952
WHERE, WHAT, OR WHY
AT THIS POINT, OKAY?

30:18.985 --> 30:20.420
IT'S ALL A BIG, PARANOID
GUESSING GAME.

30:20.453 --> 30:22.489
[ SIGHS ]
YES.

30:22.522 --> 30:25.358
BUT MAYBE SANTINO
MAY KNOW ALL THOSE THINGS

30:25.392 --> 30:27.894
BECAUSE YOU ENCOURAGED
EVERYBODY IN THIS OFFICE

30:27.927 --> 30:30.463
TO UNBURDEN THEMSELVES
TO HER.

30:30.497 --> 30:32.499
WHO KNOWS WHAT DIRTY LAUNDRY
WAS AIRED

30:32.532 --> 30:34.501
IN THE CONFINES
OF THAT OFFICE?

30:34.534 --> 30:35.969
WHAT ARE YOU
GETTING AT?

30:36.002 --> 30:37.404
LOOK...

30:37.437 --> 30:41.608
SANTINO'S LOYALTY
IS NOT TO V3.

30:41.641 --> 30:44.144
AND ONLY WHEN YOU
REALIZE THAT

30:44.177 --> 30:47.347
WILL YOU BE PROTECTING
THIS COMPANY AND YOURSELF.

30:47.380 --> 30:49.015
THINK ABOUT IT.

30:53.520 --> 30:54.654
TALKED TO MY FRIEND
AT THE BUREAU.

30:54.688 --> 30:55.955
THEY'RE ALL SET.

30:55.989 --> 30:58.058
AND YOU'RE SURE
THAT YOU CAN

30:58.091 --> 30:59.626
TRUST THIS GUY --
YOUR FRIEND?

30:59.659 --> 31:01.361
HE SAID THEY'RE WILLING
TO OFFER IMMUNITY

31:01.394 --> 31:02.395
TO ANYBODY
WHO STEPS FORWARD.

31:02.429 --> 31:03.596
IMMUNITY?

31:03.630 --> 31:05.498
SO, THEN, HE IS GONNA
HAVE TO TESTIFY

31:05.532 --> 31:06.700
AGAINST OTHER PEOPLE?

31:06.733 --> 31:08.568
WELL, TO THE EXTENT
THERE ARE OTHER PEOPLE.

31:08.601 --> 31:11.037
SO, WHERE IS THIS GUY?

31:11.071 --> 31:13.506
UH, HE SHOULD HAVE
BEEN HERE BY NOW.

31:13.540 --> 31:14.541
[ SIGHS ]

31:14.574 --> 31:15.375
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

31:15.408 --> 31:16.543
OH.

31:18.111 --> 31:20.046
[ SIGHS ]

31:20.080 --> 31:22.482
"I'VE DECIDED TO GO WITH
ONE OF MY OTHER OPTIONS.

31:22.515 --> 31:23.483
I'M SORRY."

31:24.551 --> 31:26.052
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

31:26.086 --> 31:28.088
IT MEANS THAT HE IS
A FLIGHT RISK OR WORSE,

31:28.121 --> 31:30.957
AND WE HAVE TO
FIND HIM -- NOW.

31:34.427 --> 31:37.030
[ RAP MUSIC PLAYS ]

31:37.063 --> 31:40.066
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING,
CROWD SHOUTING ]

31:40.100 --> 31:41.468
HELLO, WORLD!

31:41.501 --> 31:43.636
WELCOME TO SHE-K,

31:43.670 --> 31:46.206
LAUNCHING BRICKHOUSE LINGERIE
IN 2014.

31:46.239 --> 31:47.640
WE'RE ABOUT
TO MELT ALL THIS.

31:47.674 --> 31:49.743
THIS GUY HERE KNOWS A LOT
ABOUT LINGERIE.

31:49.776 --> 31:52.078
AND THIS IS WAY TOO MUCH
STAR POWER FOR THESE LENSES.

31:52.112 --> 31:53.413
IT'S ABOUT TO GET BURNT UP
IN HERE, BABY.

31:53.446 --> 31:55.682
WE JUST NEED
ONE FABULOUS SMILE

31:55.715 --> 31:57.183
TO LAUNCH US INTO
THE BLOGOSPHERE.

31:57.217 --> 31:58.151
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

31:58.184 --> 31:59.753
STOP CHECKING
YOUR WATCH.

31:59.786 --> 32:01.187
THERE THEY ARE!
HOW ARE YOU?

32:01.221 --> 32:02.188
HEY!

32:03.156 --> 32:04.357
GIVE ME A SMILE!
COME ON!

32:04.391 --> 32:06.059
HI!

32:06.092 --> 32:07.761
LOOK AT THE BEAUTY.
LOOK AT THE CHEMISTRY.

32:07.794 --> 32:10.363
[ LAUGHS ]
THERE YOU GO --
BRICKHOUSE BY SHE-K.

32:10.397 --> 32:12.232
LET'S GET
A SHOT TOGETHER, HUH?

32:12.265 --> 32:14.267
ALL RIGHT. THANKS.

32:14.300 --> 32:15.168
Man:
JUST A COUPLE MORE, GUYS.

32:15.201 --> 32:16.770
A QUICK PICTURE
WITH THESE YOUNG LADIES.

32:16.803 --> 32:18.471
OH, MY GOODNESS.

32:18.505 --> 32:21.408
THERE HE IS --
SUBWAY'S FAMOUS FAN!

32:21.441 --> 32:23.476
JUSTIN TUCK,
NICE TO SEE YOU.

32:23.510 --> 32:24.277
YOU'RE LOOKING GOOD.

32:24.310 --> 32:26.179
I KNOW YOU SAW
THE GAME LAST NIGHT.

32:26.212 --> 32:28.415
YEAH, YOU KIDDING ME?
FOUR SACKS? INCREDIBLE.

32:28.448 --> 32:30.250
YOU ABOUT DECAPITATED
THE QUARTERBACK.

32:30.283 --> 32:32.085
IF YOU RUN MY WAY,
YOU BETTER DUCK, BABY.

32:32.118 --> 32:33.153
[ LAUGHS ]
THIS AIN'T
TICKLEBALL.

32:33.186 --> 32:34.187
HEY,
THANKS FOR SHOWING UP.

32:35.088 --> 32:35.422
I REALLY APPRECIATE IT.
OH, MY PLEASURE.

32:36.089 --> 32:36.489
THANKS SO MUCH.
GOD BLESS.

32:37.223 --> 32:38.525
THANK YOU.
THANKS, EVERYBODY.

32:38.558 --> 32:40.126
GOD BLESS YOU.
THANK YOU.

32:40.160 --> 32:41.461
DIDN'T YOU WANT
THAT SUBWAY DEAL?

32:41.494 --> 32:44.130
YEAH -- OH, OH, I'M GONNA
GET THAT SUBWAY DEAL,

32:44.164 --> 32:45.365
BECAUSE THEY NEED SOMEBODY
LIKE THIS ON THAT.

32:45.398 --> 32:46.132
YOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?

32:47.167 --> 32:47.467
FRANK, HOW ARE YOU?
HEY, CONNOR --

32:48.301 --> 32:48.768
WHAT DO YOU HAVE TO SAY
ABOUT V3's

32:49.502 --> 32:50.170
RECENT SKIRMISH
WITH THE FBI?

32:51.137 --> 32:52.405
AH, WELL, YOU KNOW, TONIGHT,
MY ONLY CONCERN

32:52.439 --> 32:53.440
IS MAKING MONEY
FOR THE CHILDREN,

32:54.374 --> 32:55.175
AND THAT SHOULD BE YOURS,
AS WELL, FRANK.

32:56.242 --> 32:57.377
WHO TIPPED OFF THE FBI?
A DISGRUNTLED EMPLOYEE?

32:57.410 --> 32:59.279
UH, I THINK
I HEAR THE SOUND

32:59.312 --> 33:01.314
OF RAISING MONEY
FOR CHILDREN RIGHT NOW.

33:01.348 --> 33:03.316
GOOD JOB, FRANK.
THANKS, EVERYBODY.

33:03.350 --> 33:04.084
THANKS SO MUCH FOR COMING.

33:04.117 --> 33:05.285
I APPRECIATE IT.
GOD BLESS YOU.

33:08.755 --> 33:10.323
OH, THE ARTFUL DODGER.

33:10.357 --> 33:11.424
WELL...

33:11.458 --> 33:13.093
YOU CERTAINLY
HANDLED THAT WELL.

33:13.126 --> 33:14.828
OH, YOU GOT SOME BALLS
SHOWING UP.

33:14.861 --> 33:17.163
[ LAUGHS ] YOU USED TO
LIKE THAT ABOUT ME.

33:17.197 --> 33:18.531
I ALSO USED TO
LIKE FONDUE,

33:18.565 --> 33:20.166
BUT THOSE DAYS ARE LONG GONE,
AREN'T THEY?

33:20.200 --> 33:23.136
I DIDN'T COME HERE
TO FIGHT.

33:23.169 --> 33:26.439
OH. TRYING TO EASE
YOUR GUILTY CONSCIENCE?

33:26.473 --> 33:29.109
TRYING TO SUPPORT
A WORTHY CAUSE.

33:29.142 --> 33:30.543
YOU AND I MIGHT HAVE
OUR DIFFERENCES.

33:30.577 --> 33:32.379
THE FOUNDATION
ISN'T ONE OF THEM.

33:32.412 --> 33:33.813
LOOK ME IN THE EYE

33:33.847 --> 33:35.081
AND TELL ME YOU HAD
NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.

33:35.115 --> 33:36.383
[ SIGHS ]

33:36.416 --> 33:38.818
YOU NEVER DID TRUST ME.

33:38.852 --> 33:40.820
WELL, I GUESS THAT'S WHY
YOU PASSED ME OVER.

33:42.422 --> 33:44.791
AND YOU DIDN'T
ANSWER MY QUESTION.

33:58.138 --> 33:59.372
WELL?

33:59.406 --> 34:00.507
NOT IN HIS APARTMENT.

34:00.540 --> 34:01.608
YOU WENT INSIDE?

34:01.641 --> 34:03.109
OF COURSE.

34:04.144 --> 34:06.346
AND THERE'S NO RECORD OF HIM
LEAVING THE COUNTRY?

34:06.379 --> 34:08.581
CHECKED ALL INTERNATIONAL
AND DOMESTIC FLIGHTS

34:08.615 --> 34:10.216
LEAVING
THE TRI-STATE AREA,

34:10.250 --> 34:12.385
AND TRAINS GOING TO AND FROM
MEXICO AND CANADA.

34:12.419 --> 34:13.520
NOTHING.

34:13.553 --> 34:14.587
HE DIDN'T ANSWER
YOUR CALLS?

34:14.621 --> 34:16.589
NO --
OR ANY OF MY TEXTS.

34:17.490 --> 34:19.159
TERRY, I'M NOT SURE,
BUT I THINK YOUR WIFE

34:19.192 --> 34:20.527
HAS HER HAND ON MY BUTT.

34:20.560 --> 34:22.429
TERRY, THAT'S YOU!
TERRY!

34:22.462 --> 34:24.264
I'M SO SORRY
TO INTERRUPT YOU GUYS,

34:24.297 --> 34:26.166
BUT I NEED TO BORROW THE MAN
OF THE HOUR FOR JUST A MOMENT.

34:26.199 --> 34:27.567
OKAY. HEY, TERRY,
THANKS FOR ALL YOU DO.

34:27.600 --> 34:29.269
I REALLY APPRECIATE IT.
GOD BLESS YOU GUYS.

34:29.302 --> 34:30.236
THANKS.

34:30.270 --> 34:31.571
[ LAUGHTER ]

34:31.604 --> 34:33.573
YOU SEEM TO BE IN A GOOD MOOD,
CONSIDERING.

34:33.606 --> 34:34.808
AM I SUPPOSED
TO BE SCOWLING

34:34.841 --> 34:36.142
AND SCARE AWAY
ALL OUR BIG DONORS?

34:36.176 --> 34:37.210
WELL,
FAR BE IT FROM ME

34:37.243 --> 34:38.244
TO RAIN ON YOUR PARADE,

34:38.278 --> 34:39.546
BUT WE HAVE
ANOTHER PROBLEM.

34:39.579 --> 34:41.214
YEAH? WHAT'S THAT?

34:41.247 --> 34:42.148
CARL WEBBER'S NOT COMING.

34:43.450 --> 34:44.818
WHERE THE HELL IS HE?

34:44.851 --> 34:46.353
HE TEXTED ME.

34:46.386 --> 34:47.921
HE'S GOT THE FLU.

34:47.954 --> 34:50.357
ALL RIGHT.
HAVE NICO TRACK HIM DOWN.

34:50.390 --> 34:51.458
GET HIM HERE -- NOW.

34:51.491 --> 34:52.625
YOU GOT IT.

34:52.659 --> 34:54.260
[ SIGHS ]

34:54.294 --> 34:56.296
TINY! MY MAN!

34:56.329 --> 34:58.331
THANKS FOR SHOWING UP,
BROTHER. THANK YOU.

34:58.365 --> 35:01.334
[ APPLAUSE ]

35:01.368 --> 35:02.669
GOOD EVENING,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

35:02.702 --> 35:04.170
I WANT TO THANK YOU ALL
FOR ATTENDING

35:04.204 --> 35:06.272
WHAT'S TURNED OUT TO BE
V3 FOUNDATION'S

35:06.306 --> 35:07.841
MOST SUCCESSFUL EVENT YET.

35:07.874 --> 35:10.577
[ APPLAUSE ]

35:15.515 --> 35:17.851
NOW, I'D BE A FOOL
IF I DIDN'T THINK

35:17.884 --> 35:18.752
YOU WERE ALL
CHIT-CHATTING ABOUT

35:18.785 --> 35:20.620
ANOTHER EVENT
THAT HAPPENED RECENTLY,

35:20.653 --> 35:22.422
BUT I'M HERE
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH.

35:22.455 --> 35:24.958
THE CHOCOLATE CAKE WOLFGANG PUCK
PREPARED FOR US TONIGHT

35:24.991 --> 35:26.493
IS NOT ACTUALLY FAT-FREE.

35:26.526 --> 35:28.395
[ LAUGHTER ]

35:28.428 --> 35:30.430
EVERYTHING OKAY?

35:30.463 --> 35:32.232
I HOPE SO.

35:32.265 --> 35:33.933
ALL KIDDING ASIDE,
THE PROBLEMS CHILDREN FACE

35:33.967 --> 35:36.603
AROUND THE WORLD
ARE VERY SERIOUS.

35:36.636 --> 35:40.974
POVERTY, HUNGER, LACK
OF EDUCATION AND HEALTHCARE --

35:41.007 --> 35:42.642
THESE ARE THE THINGS
V3 FOUNDATION

35:42.676 --> 35:43.710
STRIVES TO MAKE
A DIFFERENCE IN.

35:43.743 --> 35:46.579
I'M HAPPY TO REPORT
THAT TONIGHT

35:46.613 --> 35:48.615
WE'VE RAISED OVER $2 MILLION
IN OUR FIGHT,

35:48.648 --> 35:50.450
AND THE NIGHT HAS JUST BEGUN.

35:50.483 --> 35:51.451
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

35:51.484 --> 35:53.620
I GOT TO HIT IT.

35:53.653 --> 35:55.555
YOU CAN'T LEAVE
DURING CONNOR'S SPEECH

35:55.588 --> 35:57.424
ABOUT SICK
AND IMPOVERISHED CHILDREN.

35:57.457 --> 35:58.491
WHAT KIND OF MESSAGE
DOES THAT SEND?

35:59.459 --> 36:00.360
SENDS THE MESSAGE THAT
HE'S TAKING WAY TOO LONG

36:01.161 --> 36:01.461
TALKING ABOUT SICK
AND POOR KIDS.

36:02.028 --> 36:03.363
OKAY, T.K., CALM DOWN.

36:04.431 --> 36:04.898
WHETHER HELPING NEEDY KIDS
HALFWAY AROUND THE WORLD

36:05.699 --> 36:06.533
OR FORGING YOUNG HEARTS
AND MINDS

36:07.200 --> 36:08.601
IN OUR VERY OWN V3 ACADEMY,

36:08.635 --> 36:09.903
NOBODY DOES IT ALONE.

36:09.936 --> 36:11.504
IT TAKES TEAMWORK,

36:11.538 --> 36:13.606
AND SOMETIMES
EVEN OUR ADVERSARIES

36:13.640 --> 36:16.576
BECOME UNLIKELY BEDFELLOWS,

36:16.609 --> 36:19.512
ALL TO SERVE
THE GREATER GOOD.

36:19.546 --> 36:21.748
AND BEFORE WE HEAD UP
TO THE ROOF FOR DINNER,

36:21.781 --> 36:24.417
I CAN THINK OF NO GREATER GOOD
THAN HANDING OVER THE MICROPHONE

36:24.451 --> 36:26.353
TO THE MAN
WE'VE ALL BEEN WAITING FOR,

36:26.386 --> 36:29.356
V3's MOST GENEROUS,
NOT TO MENTION BIGGEST, DONOR,

36:29.389 --> 36:31.591
IN EVERY WAY,
SHAPE, AND FORM.

36:31.624 --> 36:33.626
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
MR. SHAQUILLE O'NEAL.

36:33.660 --> 36:34.694
SHAQ, COME ON OUT!

36:34.728 --> 36:36.329
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

36:36.363 --> 36:39.366
VALET'S TAKING FOREVER!

36:39.399 --> 36:41.701
I KNEW THIS PLAN WAS BRAIN DEAD
FROM THE START.

36:41.735 --> 36:44.437
OH, I WILL SHOW YOU
BRAIN DEAD, CINDERFELLA.

36:44.471 --> 36:45.772
WHAT?
YOU THINK THIS IS --

36:45.805 --> 36:46.940
WH-WHERE
ARE YOU GOING?

36:46.973 --> 36:49.275
TO FIND US A PUMPKIN.

36:49.309 --> 36:51.311
WHAT?

36:51.344 --> 36:54.981
CARL, YOU DIDN'T SHOW,
AND I'M CONCERNED.

36:55.015 --> 36:58.018
CAN YOU PLEASE JUST LET ME KNOW
THAT YOU'RE OKAY?

36:59.452 --> 37:01.588
YOU REALLY NEVER
TURN IT OFF, DO YOU?

37:01.621 --> 37:04.057
NOT WHEN IT COMES
TO MY CLIENTS...

37:04.090 --> 37:06.393
NO.

37:06.426 --> 37:08.495
SAM, I'M --

37:08.528 --> 37:09.963
LOOK.
[ SIGHS ]

37:09.996 --> 37:11.431
I LIKE YOU.

37:11.464 --> 37:14.034
I-I REALLY DO.

37:14.067 --> 37:16.670
BUT THE CASUAL THING --

37:16.703 --> 37:18.672
IT'S NOT ME.

37:18.705 --> 37:19.973
I HAVE TROUBLE JUST --

37:20.006 --> 37:21.741
JUST BEING SUPERFICIAL?

37:21.775 --> 37:24.444
WHICH IS, O-OF COURSE,
THE REASON I LIKE YOU.

37:24.477 --> 37:26.012
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:26.046 --> 37:29.416
WELL, MAYBE I'LL SEE YOU
IN TWO YEARS.

37:29.449 --> 37:31.284
YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF, DANI.

37:35.055 --> 37:36.990
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

37:46.599 --> 37:48.501
[ ENGINE REVS ]

37:51.071 --> 37:53.406
T.K.!
HEY! T.K.!

37:53.440 --> 37:54.741
WHAT?

37:54.774 --> 37:55.809
WHOSE CAR IS THIS?

37:55.842 --> 37:57.577
I GOT NO IDEA.
COME ON. GET IN.

37:57.610 --> 37:59.446
SO, YOU'RE JUST GONNA
STEAL A MASERATI?

37:59.479 --> 38:01.715
I'M BORROWING IT. COME ON,
GET IN OR GET CUT.

38:03.149 --> 38:05.051
OKAY, YOU'RE --
YOU'RE PUTTING A BLACK DUDE

38:05.085 --> 38:07.520
IN A STOLEN VEHICLE,
'CAUSE YOU'RE CRAZY.

38:07.554 --> 38:09.055
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE CAPABLE OF ANYMORE.

38:09.089 --> 38:10.457
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE CAPABLE OF.

38:10.490 --> 38:11.624
WHOO!

38:25.171 --> 38:26.506
MR. KING.

38:26.539 --> 38:27.640
MM.

38:27.674 --> 38:29.642
9:59.

38:29.676 --> 38:31.044
CUTTING IT KIND OF CLOSE,
AREN'T WE?

38:31.077 --> 38:32.612
WELL, MY GRANDPA
ALWAYS SAYS

38:32.645 --> 38:34.147
THAT CLOSE ONLY COUNTS
IN HORSESHOES

38:34.180 --> 38:36.116
AND HAND GRENADES.
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:36.149 --> 38:38.551
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
HI. I'M SHEERA.

38:38.585 --> 38:40.653
UH, FEAR NOT, COACH.

38:40.687 --> 38:41.755
I PROMISE YOU
I'LL BE COUNTING Z's

38:41.788 --> 38:43.390
IN T-MINUS 30 SECONDS.

38:43.423 --> 38:46.159
GET YOUR ASS UPSTAIRS

38:46.192 --> 38:48.161
AND KISS YOUR LADY FRIEND
GOOD NIGHT.

38:48.194 --> 38:49.863
WITH PLEASURE.

38:51.865 --> 38:53.500
BYE.

38:53.533 --> 38:54.634
DOUCHE BAG.
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:54.668 --> 38:57.103
MM.

38:57.137 --> 38:58.471
ALL RIGHT,
I MISS YOU ALREADY.

39:00.640 --> 39:02.842
YOU KNOW SOMETHING?

39:02.876 --> 39:03.877
YOU'RE SOME KIND
OF CRAZY.

39:05.478 --> 39:06.813
BUT I DIG IT.

39:06.846 --> 39:08.815
YOU BETTER.
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:09.916 --> 39:11.418
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:15.555 --> 39:18.158
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

39:18.191 --> 39:19.793
TUCKING YOU IN.

39:27.167 --> 39:29.703
GENTLEMEN.

39:29.736 --> 39:30.704
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

39:30.737 --> 39:32.605
NO. IT'S NOT.

39:32.639 --> 39:34.441
WHY? WHAT HAPPENED?

39:35.775 --> 39:37.844
CARL WEBBER.

39:37.877 --> 39:40.680
JUMPED OFF THE ROOF
OF HIS SoHo BUILDING.

39:42.515 --> 39:43.850
HE'S DEAD.

39:52.892 --> 39:55.161
IT SEEMS CARL HAS BEEN
STEALING MONEY FROM V3.

39:55.195 --> 39:57.130
AT LEAST THAT'S
WHAT WE'RE LEARNING.

39:57.163 --> 39:59.599
APPARENTLY HE WAS INTO
SOME CREATIVE ACCOUNTING,

39:59.632 --> 40:01.101
SIPHONING FUNDS
FROM THE FOUNDATION

40:01.134 --> 40:02.836
FOR HIS OWN USE.

40:02.869 --> 40:04.738
STEALING FROM CHARITIES,
NO LESS.

40:04.771 --> 40:06.940
I'LL HAVE TO ASSUME HE WAS
THE ONE THE FBI WAS LOOKING FOR,

40:06.973 --> 40:09.609
SO I GUESS THEY GOT
ALL THEIR INFORMATION.

40:09.642 --> 40:12.612
DANI, I KNOW IT'S BEEN
A TOUGH WEEK FOR ALL OF US.

40:12.645 --> 40:14.981
EVERYONE HERE AT V3
REALLY LOVED CARL.

40:15.015 --> 40:17.083
NO MATTER WHAT HE DID,
HE WAS STILL FAMILY.

40:17.117 --> 40:19.152
PEOPLE ARE GONNA HAVE TO
DEAL WITH THEIR GRIEF.

40:19.185 --> 40:22.622
I'LL HELP
IN ANY WAY I CAN.

40:22.655 --> 40:24.257
TROY.

40:24.290 --> 40:26.760
SEND A CONDOLENCE NOTE
TO THE FAMILY.

40:26.793 --> 40:29.963
SPEAKING OF NOTES,
DID CARL LEAVE ONE?

40:29.996 --> 40:32.866
FROM WHAT
WE UNDERSTAND, NO.

40:32.899 --> 40:34.200
CARL HAD
A STORY TO TELL.

40:34.234 --> 40:35.969
I GUESS WE'LL NEVER KNOW
WHAT IT WAS.

40:44.944 --> 40:46.212
DANI.

40:46.246 --> 40:47.747
YOU ALL RIGHT?

40:47.781 --> 40:50.250
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I AM RIGHT NOW.

40:50.283 --> 40:52.719
THIS IS NOT ON YOU.

40:52.752 --> 40:55.955
YOU DID EVERYTHING
YOU COULD.

40:55.989 --> 40:57.157
DID I?

40:57.190 --> 41:00.760
* WILL YOU SHINE

41:00.794 --> 41:05.265
* LIKE A JEWEL

41:05.298 --> 41:09.302
* IN THE MORNING

41:09.336 --> 41:14.274
* IN THE MORNING

41:14.307 --> 41:17.677
* BUT YOU'RE SHY

41:17.711 --> 41:23.116
* AND YOU'RE CRUEL

41:23.149 --> 41:27.120
* WERE YOU LONELY?

41:27.153 --> 41:30.156
* WERE YOU LONELY?

41:30.190 --> 41:34.027
[ SNIFFLES ]
